00:01:13.570 --> 00:01:14.570
ADVANTAGES OF HANGING DRESS SHIRTS

00:01:14.570 --> 00:01:15.570
Dry shirt

00:01:15.570 --> 00:01:19.580
If you want to hang up your shirts, here are
the advantages of hanging up your shirt.

00:01:19.580 --> 00:01:26.450
If you hang up your shirt, you know that it's
going to be dry, and why is this important?

00:01:26.450 --> 00:01:32.250
Because most shirts are made out of cotton
and if you put away a shirt damp or wet or

00:01:32.250 --> 00:01:37.000
there's somehow moisture getting into your
drawer, you will get mildew and it will eat

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.270
and destroy the cotton.

00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:39.460
It's one of the few things.

00:01:39.460 --> 00:01:44.610
You don't have to worry about moths with cotton,
but you do have to worry about mildew.

00:01:44.610 --> 00:01:49.600
So if your shirt is hanging up there, most
likely it's going to be dry.

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:50.700
Wrinkle-free

00:01:50.700 --> 00:01:55.740
If the shirt just came back from the cleaners
or you just ironed it and it looks great for

00:01:55.740 --> 00:02:00.090
the week, you put it on a hanger and most
likely, unless your three-year-old gets a

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:05.810
hold of it and pulls it down and uses it as
a blanket, it is going to stay wrinkle-free,

00:02:05.810 --> 00:02:09.429
so another great reason to put it on the hanger.

00:02:09.429 --> 00:02:10.899
Easier to sort through

00:02:10.899 --> 00:02:11.959
Let's say you've got a jacket.

00:02:11.959 --> 00:02:16.569
You want to see, "Okay, I really want to wear
this jacket or this tie," and you can then

00:02:16.569 --> 00:02:21.680
hold it up to all of the shirts looking through
your wardrobe, so there's another reason.

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:23.209
Easier to put away

00:02:23.209 --> 00:02:27.840
Let's say you wear this shirt for an hour,
a couple of hours, and it's perfectly clean.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.840
You take it off, easily put it back on the
hanger.

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:32.190
That takes a couple of seconds.

00:02:32.190 --> 00:02:33.230
ADVANTAGES OF FOLDING DRESS SHIRTS

00:02:33.230 --> 00:02:36.540
Now, why would you want to then fold your
